Author: hebanwbs
Text: Thanks a lot that is very relieving to hear and I might do that

Author: LowCalPal
Text: You are fortunate that you got help so quickly!  I understand why you would be worried, eating disorders are serious business.  In your case, you are most likely safe; our bodies are very resilient and it would be difficult to do any permanent damage in just a few months.  It might set your mind at ease if you went to the doctor and asked for a full physical.  It's something that needs to be done periodically anyway, and then, just as you say, you'd be able to move forward.
